Function Description <code>http.get(string url)</code> Send a GET request <code>http.post(string url, string body, dict headers)</code> Send a POST request <code>http.put(string url, string body, dict headers)</code> Send a PUT request <code>http.delete(string url)</code> Send a DELETE request <p>All request functions return a response dict:</p> <pre><code>{
    "status": 200,
    "body": "...",
    "headers": {"content-type": "application/json", ...}
}
</code></pre>
